<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Open the door to OpenRoaming!</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
</head>
<body class="bg-[#080D4A]">
<div class="container mx-auto px-8 pb-8 pt-[50px]">
    <div class="bg-white rounded-[18px] p-6 shadow-md">
        <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold">Password Reset Request - OpenRoaming Portal</h1>
        <p class="mt-6 text-lg">
            To confirm your password reset request, please follow these steps:
        </p>
        <ol class="mt-2 text-lg list-decimal list-inside">
            <li>Register the new temporary password: <strong>{{ currentPassword }}</strong></li>
            <li>Click
                <a class="font-bold text-[#7BBA29] underline"
                   href="{{ absolute_url('/login/link') ~ '?' ~ 'uuid=' ~ uuid|url_encode ~ '&verificationCode=' ~ verificationCode }}">
                    here
                </a>
                to proceed and validate your account
            </li>
            <li>Log in using the temporary password provided above, then set a new password</li>
            <li>Download your OpenRoaming profile</li>
        </ol>
        <p class="mt-6 text-lg">
            Thank you,<br>
            OpenRoaming Portal Support Team
        </p>
    </div>
</div>
</body>
</html>
